{
  "name": "w06_b05_04.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "line": "しばらくみこと姉ちゃんと甘い時間を過ごしてから……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "line": "夜がすっかり更けていることに気づいて、大急ぎで\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "line": "片付けをして、厨房を出た。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "line": "部屋に戻ってくると、急に眠気が襲ってきて……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "line": "俺はあくびを噛み殺しながら、すでに寝ているらしい\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "line": "智花の後ろで寝間着に着替えた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "line": "いつもなら父さんたちの部屋へ行って着替えるのだが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "line": "今日だけは許してもらうことにした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "line": "「よい……しょっと」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "line": "ベッドに入って、もぞもぞと身体の位置を調整する。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "line": "さあ、これで寝る準備は整った——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020108\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "line": "「ねえ、和哉」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "「っっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "line": "寝ていると思っていた智花からはっきりと呼びかけられて、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "line": "心臓が震えあがった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020109\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "line": "「な、なによ、どうしてそんなにびくっとするわけ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "line": "くるりと反転して俺の方へ顔を向けた智花は、眠っていた\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "line": "様子がみじんもない平常の顔をしていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "line": "「もう寝てるのかと思ってたんだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020110\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "line": "「ふぅん、だからこの部屋で着替えたわけね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "line": "「うっ、ごめん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020111\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "line": "「別にいいわよ、私は見てなかったわけだし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "line": "智花が微苦笑を浮かべる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "line": "普段とはわずかに違った反応に違和感を覚えた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "line": "「どうかしたのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020112\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "line": "「……どうかって？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "line": "慎重に、探るような声だった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "line": "「いつもの智花と様子が違うからさ。なにかあったのかと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "line": "　思って」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020113\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "line": "智花は静かな表情で、じっと俺を見つめる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020114\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "line": "「……和哉は」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 156,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "line": "ぽつり、と智花がつぶやいた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "line": "長いまつげが伏せられて、表情がかげる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020115\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "line": "「母さんの言ったこと……どう思ってるの？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 168,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 169,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 172,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020116\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 173,
      "line": "「和哉が私を分かってくれてるように、私も和哉のことを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 174,
      "line": "　分かってるつもりだった」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 177,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020117\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 178,
      "line": "「でも……最近は違うのよ……和哉がどんなことを考えて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179,
      "line": "　いるのかわからなくて……やきもきするの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 183,
      "line": "痛みをこらえるように、智花が胸の上へ手を置いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 187,
      "line": "「それは……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 192,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020118\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 193,
      "line": "「和哉は……誰か一人を選ぼうとしてるの？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 196,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 197,
      "line": "智花の瞳は伏せられていて、普段の強気な光は\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 198,
      "line": "見られなかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 201,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 202,
      "line": "「俺は……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 212,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 213,
      "line": "先刻まで一緒に居た、みこと姉ちゃんの姿が脳裏をよぎる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 216,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 217,
      "line": "俺が他の姉妹を退けて、みこと姉ちゃんを選ぶことを……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "彼女は受け入れてくれるだろうか？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 221,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 222,
      "line": "そもそも俺自身に、他の姉妹を退け……傷つける決意が、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "あるだろうか？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 231,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020119\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232,
      "line": "「和哉……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 235,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 236,
      "line": "智花はいつの間にか顔をあげて、俺を見つめていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 239,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 240,
      "line": "生まれた時から、ずっと一緒にいる家族。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 243,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 244,
      "line": "六人でいろいろなことを話して、感じて、共有して……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 247,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 248,
      "line": "そしてなにより智花は、こうしてこの年まで同じベッドで\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 249,
      "line": "寝ているくらい、自分の分身のような存在で……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 252,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253,
      "line": "「……分からない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 256,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 257,
      "line": "ぐるぐると渦巻く思考に、まだ答えは出せそうになかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 262,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020120\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263,
      "line": "「……そう、なの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 266,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 267,
      "line": "智花は、問いかけたときと同じようにぽつりとつぶやき、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 268,
      "line": "頷いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 271,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 272,
      "line": "断罪を免れたような、先延ばしになったことを憂うような、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 273,
      "line": "あいまいな表情を浮かべている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 277,
      "line": "「……ごめん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 282,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020121\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 283,
      "line": "「和哉が優柔不断なのは、じゅううっぶん分かってるわ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 286,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 287,
      "line": "「うっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "にやりと笑う智花に、なんの反論もできない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 294,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020122\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 295,
      "line": "「釈然とはしないけど、とりあえずはすっきりしたわ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 298,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 299,
      "line": "「そうか……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 302,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020123\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 303,
      "line": "「でも……忘れないでね。時間はほとんど残っていない\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 304,
      "line": "　のよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 307,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 308,
      "line": "「ああ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 313,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020124\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 314,
      "line": "「……そんなに暗い顔させるつもりじゃなかったのよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 317,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020125\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 318,
      "line": "「不安を押し付けて、ごめんね和哉」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 324,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 325,
      "line": "きゅっと鼻をつままれる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 330,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 331,
      "line": "「もが」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM020126\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 335,
      "line": "「こうしてれば、よく眠れるんじゃない？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 338,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 339,
      "line": "「それは眠るんじゃなくて酸欠で気絶してるんだよ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 343,
      "line": "智花はひとしきりころころと笑ったあと、再び寝返りを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 344,
      "line": "うって背中を向けた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 355,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 356,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 359,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 360,
      "line": "姉妹の中から、誰か一人を選ぶ——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 363,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 364,
      "line": "自分の人生の決定打となるような選択に、心臓がごとりと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 365,
      "line": "嫌な震え方をする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 368,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 369,
      "line": "そんな選択を迫られていることに理不尽さを覚えながらも、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 370,
      "line": "俺は腹を据える決意を徐々に固めていった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 373,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 374,
      "line": "時計の音が、やけに耳に残る夜だった。\r\n"
    }
  ]
}